title: [Western Waterway, Charl's Teeth]
description: Along the horizon to the south, a large dark spire rises from the ocean to tower into the sky.  Tiny whitecaps dance about, lit from the moon high above.  A large dark form of seaweed floats on the surface nearby, the moonlight glinting off the thin tendrils.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, east, west, northwest
